msgctxt "734\t866"
msgid ""
"You wasted no time in getting here...\\n"
"Chairman Dojima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "996\t1056"
msgid "Arai."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1064\t1128"
msgid "I knew you'd come."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1155\t1327"
msgid ""
"After all, you're the one who's\\n"
"been engineering Kido's every move."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1375\t1470"
msgid "Isn't that right, Kido!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1627\t1713"
msgid "Forgive me, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1767\t1839"
msgid "How long have you known?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1852\t1956"
msgid "Since Kido told me about the 100 billion."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1970\t2118"
msgid ""
"He wanted to steal Akiyama-san's money,\\n"
"pretend to turn it over to Katsuragi..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2119\t2283"
msgid ""
"Then invest in Munakata's master plan.\\n"
"Or so he claimed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2308\t2405"
msgid "Kido is my trusted sworn brother."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2406\t2577"
msgid ""
"But he couldn't possibly have\\n"
"known of my link to Munakata."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2614\t2737"
msgid "Someone else must have filled him in on the details."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2751\t2809"
msgid "And that, Daigo-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2812\t2867"
msgid "Must have been you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2875\t2935"
msgid "Fair enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2962\t3139"
msgid ""
"You nudged Kido closer to Katsuragi.\\n"
"Had him squeal about the 100 billion."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3174\t3346"
msgid ""
"Katsuragi, desperate after Munakata abandoned him,\\n"
"was all too easy to manipulate into slipping up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3363\t3522"
msgid ""
"And that slip up indeed came...\\n"
"when the Ueno Seiwa fell by Kiryu-san's hand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3523\t3638"
msgid "Without even the slightest support from Munakata."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3669\t3747"
msgid "But something derailed your plan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3776\t3847"
msgid "The death of Yasuko Saejima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3906\t4061"
msgid ""
"If she had only survived,\\n"
"everything would have gone off without a hitch."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4077\t4299"
msgid ""
"After all, with no reason left to fight,\\n"
"Kiryu and Saejima would have left Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4383\t4499"
msgid ""
"Impressive.\\n"
"You figured all that out?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4533\t4697"
msgid ""
"Not without some help from Kido here.\\n"
"He confirmed my suspicions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4708\t4879"
msgid ""
"I knew if I let him live,\\n"
"he'd end up running straight into your arms."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5058\t5122"
msgid "So, when was it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5133\t5254"
msgid ""
"When did you decide to betray\\n"
"the Tojo to get at this money?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5287\t5358"
msgid "Betrayal, you say?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5366\t5506"
msgid ""
"But of course.\\n"
"There's no other word for it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5518\t5699"
msgid ""
"You've spat on Kiryu-san and Kazama-san's legacy.\\n"
"And everyone else who had made the Tojo Clan great."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5712\t5812"
msgid ""
"You even served Majima-san\\n"
"to Munakata on a silver platter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5832\t5878"
msgid "All that for this pile of cash?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5879\t5945"
msgid "You don't know a damn thing!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6021\t6084"
msgid "The clan isn't what it used to be."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6107\t6330"
msgid ""
"We have over 100 families. 30,000 men.\\n"
"Do you know what it takes to keep order in that chaos!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6361\t6421"
msgid "Chairman..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6447\t6629"
msgid ""
"We've always had heroes like Kiryu-san to protect us.\\n"
"That's how the Tojo has lasted so long."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6644\t6722"
msgid "But we've reached our limit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6746\t6901"
msgid ""
"I have to rebuild from the ground up,\\n"
"even if that means making sacrifices along the way!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6916\t7058"
msgid ""
"Sacrifices like throwing Majima\\n"
"to the police department wolves!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7064\t7149"
msgid "This is all wrong, Daigo-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7159\t7228"
msgid "It's for the good of the clan!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7243\t7323"
msgid "If I don't keep it safe, who will!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7332\t7408"
msgid "You don't have what it takes, Arai!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7506\t7626"
msgid ""
"Besides, you're not going\\n"
"about this any better than me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7646\t7831"
msgid ""
"You talk like you're the perfect yakuza,\\n"
"but you're just another police whipping boy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7958\t8018"
msgid "Touch√©."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8032\t8110"
msgid "But I'm no whipping boy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8309\t8353"
msgid "What the!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8384\t8481"
msgid "Hold on. That would mean..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8503\t8560"
msgid "Yes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8565\t8680"
msgid ""
"I'm not yakuza.\\n"
"Never have been."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8695\t8831"
msgid ""
"I'm an undercover agent sent by\\n"
"Munakata to investigate the Tojo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8839\t8914"
msgid "And to seize control of the clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8934\t9027"
msgid "Aniki, you're a cop?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9037\t9093"
msgid "I was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9098\t9168"
msgid "But that too is in the past!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9192\t9299"
msgid "I betrayed Munakata. Ended his life!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9310\t9409"
msgid ""
"You see, Daigo-san?\\n"
"I'm not like you at all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9504\t9629"
msgid ""
"I'll bring my justice to the world,\\n"
"even if I have to fight fate itself!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9640\t9705"
msgid "And this money'll help me do it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9708\t9764"
msgid "Fool."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9895\t10062"
msgid ""
"Through the millennia of human history,\\n"
"one truth has been made clear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10566\t10656"
msgid "There's no overcoming your station in life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10662\t10848"
msgid ""
"Power has always reigned supreme.\\n"
"Some use, while all others become the used."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10860\t10986"
msgid ""
"Deputy Commissioner?\\n"
"How are you still alive?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11267\t11327"
msgid "Painful, yes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11358\t11425"
msgid "But it's far from lethal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11429\t11501"
msgid "A truly amazing technology."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11506\t11601"
msgid "Vastly improved in the past 25 years."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11611\t11650"
msgid "Explain."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11664\t11765"
msgid "These are non-lethal riot control rounds."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11766\t11837"
msgid "Highly advanced rubber bullets."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11856\t11999"
msgid "Then the rounds in the gun I shot you with..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12017\t12147"
msgid "Never had a chance of finishing the job."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12317\t12429"
msgid ""
"Your lack of finesse is\\n"
"what holds you back, Arai-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12434\t12520"
msgid "Justice is far beyond your reach."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12545\t12667"
msgid ""
"Oh, and Dojima-san.\\n"
"The same goes for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12688\t12848"
msgid ""
"Keeping the Tojo Clan afloat must be\\n"
"difficult for a man of your inferior caliber."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12924\t13143"
msgid ""
"And you. Stumbling across that 100 billion\\n"
"must have felt like a dream come true."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13155\t13239"
msgid "Not that dreams are a bad thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13244\t13320"
msgid "I can forgive you for that, at least."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13341\t13386"
msgid "Munakata..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13430\t13557"
msgid "The men before you are my loyal servants."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13602\t13678"
msgid "You all die here today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13703\t13865"
msgid ""
"I won't let anyone get in\\n"
"the way of my grand ideals."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14579\t14623"
msgid "The money!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14638\t14750"
msgid ""
"Don't just stand there, you fools!\\n"
"Do something!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14895\t14982"
msgid ""
"What are you doing?\\n"
"Shoot that thing down!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15995\t16055"
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16468\t16582"
msgid "Okay, everyone pick an ass to kick."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16840\t16900"
msgid "Kido-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16909\t16976"
msgid "When you were flounderin'..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16977\t17083"
msgid ""
"I told ya to go balls out.\\n"
"No regrets."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17102\t17252"
msgid "Only fair I practice what I preach now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17285\t17345"
msgid "Saejima-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17473\t17557"
msgid "This is all my fault."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17595\t17743"
msgid ""
"I'm the one who forced the Tojo Clan on you.\\n"
"Left you on your own."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17746\t17857"
msgid "But now... I'm done running."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17881\t17974"
msgid "It's time I take responsibility for my mistakes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18024\t18084"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18154\t18214"
msgid "You're..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18227\t18382"
msgid ""
"The detective you thought Hisai-san\\n"
"rubbed out of the picture. Name's Tanimura."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18398\t18609"
msgid ""
"I hate people like you.\\n"
"Can't survive without others to do your dirty work."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18626\t18770"
msgid ""
"After the living hell you put\\n"
"Sugiuchi-san and Hisai-san through..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18775\t18874"
msgid "I'm gonna put you away for a long time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18883\t18947"
msgid "You arrogant brat...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19028\t19128"
msgid "Flashy as always, Akiyama-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19160\t19219"
msgid "I'm kinda relieved."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19220\t19359"
msgid ""
"I was really starting to doubt\\n"
"my ability to judge people's characters."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19368\t19476"
msgid "Turns out you dream even bigger than I expected."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19583\t19683"
msgid "You get points for ditching Munakata."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19684\t19834"
msgid ""
"But claiming justice while you're pinching\\n"
"someone else's cash is just bullshit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19860\t19945"
msgid "So I'm gonna have to stop you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19977\t20025"
msgid "You can try."
msgstr ""